1) Ballot Box,an online voting system which holds all the features no less than electronic voting.
2) First step for the user is to sign up with the application.
3) user security has been provided by email verification as well as face recognition feature which stops the application from fraud usage.
4) Voter can select the candidate he is interested to vote for.(voter can vote only once for a single candidate).
5) In order to advertise about his stand, candidate can upate about his campaigning.
6) Interested user can volunteer for campaigning by registering as a volunteer.
7) Candidate can provide relative blurb to the admin.
